data.description: Welcome Home to the Traditions of Braselton Community!   This home greets you with natural light flowing throughout. The Main Floor hosts an Open Concept layout with many builder upgrades! The kitchen has white Cabinets, white granite counter tops, beautiful backsplash, Stainless Steel Appliances, and a walk in Pantry.   Entering the Living area, you will feel right at home with the cozy electric fireplace!   Step outside onto the deck that has been extended with stairs leading to the spacious, fenced in backyard.  The Upper level of the home welcomes you with three bedrooms AND an oversized entertainment loft that is a perfect place for a game room, playroom, or office. The Large Primary Suite has trayed ceilings and a beautiful master bathroom with a huge walk-in closet. Laundry is conveniently located upstairs along with the two secondary bedrooms. The basement is unfinished and ready for your customization!  This Home is located in a Golf/Tennis Community with RESORT STYLE LIVING including a clubhouse, gym, pool, nature trails, pickleball courts, restaurant, and many more amenities!
